1. Download and install Grails 1.1.2. Set GRAILS_HOME and add 
   and add $GRAILS_HOME/bin to your $PATH.

     http://grails.org/Download

2. Download the oauth-plugin for Grails.

     http://github.com/mraible/grails-oauth/zipball/master

3. Extract the plugin and build it.

     grails package-plugin

4. Install the plugin in this project.

     grails install-plugin path/to/zip

5. Create LinkedIn API keys at http://developer.linkedin.com/community/apis 
   and set your callback URL to be:

     http://localhost:8080/grails-oauth/oauth/callback

6. Run "grails run-app" and enjoy. 
